    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered for the serious driver is this E92-generation BMW M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, an engine characterized by its eight individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear-axle M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution during high-lateral-G cornering. The chassis integrity is excellent, retaining its factory-spec aluminum multi-link suspension and carbon fiber roof for a reduced polar moment of inertia. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring the internal tolerances remain within peak operating parameters. With its communicative hydraulic steering rack and linear power delivery, this M3 represents a tactile mechanical experience that modern EPS-equipped vehicles cannot match.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
