    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a meticulously maintained luxury SUV that perfectly balances comfort and performance. The Atomic Silver exterior retains a deep, showroom-quality gloss, accented by 20-inch split-five-spoke alloy wheels. While the body is in excellent shape overall, there is a minor, professionally touched-up scuff on the lower rear bumper and one small door ding on the passenger side\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is smoke-free and plush; the only sign of use is light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. This vehicle comes fully loaded with the Premium Package, featuring a power moonroof, heated and ventilated front seats, and a wood-trimmed steering wheel. Mechanically, it is robust and ready for the road, backed by a complete service history. We recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes are sharp and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It\u2019s a sophisticated, turnkey vehicle for a discerning buyer.",
